<div class="i-container text-center">
  <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
    <div class="text-left half-screen">
      <h1 class="logo font-weight-bold">SimpleSaver</h1><br>
      <p>Lorem ipsum is placeholder text commonly used in the graphic, print, and publishing industries for     previewing   layouts and visual mockups.</p>
    </div>
    <%= image_tag "i-screen.png", height: "350px" %>
  </div>
</div>

  <div class="step-cards py-2">
    <div class="i-container text-center">
      <h2 class="pb-4">Save automatically and reach your financial goals<br> in 3 simple steps!</h2>
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mt-5">
        <div class="i-step">
          <%= image_tag "SimpleSaverMoney.svg", height: "60px", class: "mb-2 icon-bw" %>
          <h5 class="font-weight-bold">Add a budget</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="i-step">
          <%= image_tag "SimpleSaverTarget.svg", height: "60px", class: "mb-2 icon-bw" %>
          <h5 class="font-weight-bold">Set a goal</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="i-step">
          <%= image_tag "SimpleSaverPiggy.svg", height: "60px", class: "mb-2 icon-bw" %>
          <h5 class="font-weight-bold">Save the difference</h5>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<div class="i-container text-center">
  <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
    <div class="i-text text-left half-screen">
      <h3 class="font-weight-bold mt-2" id="type-1"></h3>
      <p>First select an expense category you would like to track. Maybe coffee?</p>
      <p>You choose to track your expenses monthly, for a weekend or as long as you want.</p>
      <p>Set a budget you think you can beat. Be sure itâ€™s a challenge. </p>
    </div>
    <%= image_tag "i-desk.png", height: "200px", class: "half-screen img-right img-shadow" %>
  </div>
  <hr>

  <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
    <%= image_tag "i-couch.png", height: "200px", class: "half-screen img-left img-shadow" %>
    <div class="i-text text-left half-screen ml-5">
      <h3 class="font-weight-bold mt-2" id="type-2"></h3>
      <p>Continue by choosing a goal you want to save towards, and set a budget.</p>
      <p>Saving is easier, fun and rewarding when you know what you're doing it for.</p>
      <p>Your goal can be antyhing. How does a gap year in Australia sounds like?</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr>

  <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mb-5">
    <div class="i-text text-left half-screen">
      <p>Your setup is done! Simplesaver will track your spending and provide feedback to help you stick with your goals.</p>
      <p>Saving has never been easier! Click on the button below to kickstart your account and start your journey. </p>
      <h3 class="call font-weight-bold mt-5" id="type-hs"></h3>
